<br>
This is my second Bard that I have leveled up in the game.  My other Bard is a level 63 Vah Shir with his epic and a full set of HoT armor on Sullon Zek.  I have already acquired several of my mob drop songs including Occlusion of Sound.  Here is the link to my <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=776381" target="top"><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Magelo</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> if you are interested.<br>
<br>
I’m looking for a guild that has a nice mix between raiding, grouping/LDoN and solo play.  I enjoy doing the quests in the game and have started several including; coldain shawl and ring, Qeynos badge of honor, Eye Patch of Plunder, some LoY quests, epic and I'm sure I have pieces for others also.  I also already have CoV faction of amiable for access to ToV for HoT raids.  And I am keyed to Sebalis.<br>
<br>
I'm not much of a role player, but being a bard I don't normally say much anyway.  (Too busy weaving songs to type most of the time.)  I do play a lot and can be found in game most weekdays from 6 pm to 11 pm Mountain Standard Time and just about anytime during the weekend.<br>
<br>
You can leave a message here or shot me a tell in game if you are interested.  Don’t be offended if I don’t respond immediately or just shot back a tell saying “Sec”.  I often experience by train kiting and it might be awhile before I can kill everything or make a run to a zone line without killing everyone else in the zone.  I will get back to you eventually.<br>
<br>
Thanks for taking a look and safe journey to you,<br>
Rokr<br>
